title: Camco Heavy-Duty Leveling Blocks | Compatible with Single Wheels, Double Wheels, Hydraulic Jacks, Tongue Jacks and More | Yellow | 10-pack (44510) - Design May Vary
description: Camco’s Heavy-Duty Leveling Blocks allow you to stack interlocking blocks to the desired height for safe and easy leveling. Each block adds a full inch to the stack height. These leveling blocks are compatible with single wheels, double wheels, hydraulic jacks, tongue jacks, stabilizer jacks, fifth wheel jacks and tandem axles. They are made of durable resin. Each block measures 8 ½-inches x 8 ½-inches x 1 ½-inch. As the blocks are nested together, each block adds 1-inch of additional height. Includes a zippered storage bag with handle for convenient storage and transportation. The stack height should not exceed four blocks. Proudly made in the USA.
